      "span_text": "For surgical patients the pharmacokinetic data of rocuronium were derived from a study in which rocuronium was administered as a bolus dose of 600 g kg 91 followed by a continuous infusion to maintain twitch height at 10% of control. The mean pharmacokinetic variables of a twoexponential model were: clearance 4.51 ml kg 91 min 91, intercompartmental clearance 1.77 ml kg 91 min 91, V c 146 ml kg 91 and V ss 310 ml kg 91."
